                "title": "Minimum Wage Requirements",
                "data": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "data": "In Japan, the minimum wage is complex. The minimum hourly wage is set according to the region of the employee, and it can vary between ¥714 and ¥1023."
                    }
